premise_source_doc_sentence: La La Land received the most nominations in eleven categories , including Best Film , Best Director  (  Damien Chazelle  )  , Best Actor in a Leading Role  (  Ryan Gosling  )  , Best Actress in a Leading Role  (  Emma Stone  )  , and Best Original Screenplay  (  Chazelle  )  .
